经常要用防忘记的一些指令

直接运行
qemu-system-riscv32 -machine virt -nographic -bios none -kernel test-assemble -S -s

调试
qemu-system-riscv32 -machine virt -nographic -bios none -kernel test-assemble -S -s
gdb-multiarch -ex "target remote :1234"


反汇编查看
qemu-system-riscv32 \
 -machine virt \
 -nographic \
 -bios none \
 -kernel test-assemble \
 -d in_asm

gdb常用

set $pc = 0x80000000
x/10i $pc